{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EnvironmentValues"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/environmentvalues\/minimumscalefactor"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EnvironmentValues\/minimumScaleFactor"},"abstract":[{"text":"The minimum permissible proportion to shrink the font size to fit","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the text into the available space.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"6.0","beta":false}],"title":"minimumScaleFactor","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore17EnvironmentValuesV18minimumScaleFactor14CoreFoundation7CGFloatVvp","role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/View\/Text\/Util\/EnvironmentParagraphStyle.swift#L309","fileName":"EnvironmentParagraphStyle.swift"},"symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"minimumScaleFactor","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"minimumScaleFactor"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the example below, a label with a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"minimumScaleFactor"},{"type":"text","text":" of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.5"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"draws its text in a font size as small as half of the actual font if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"needed to fit into the space next to the text input field:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["HStack {","    Text(\"This is a very long label:\")","        .lineLimit(1)","        .minimumScaleFactor(0.5)","    TextField(\"My Long Text Field\", text: $myTextField)","        .frame(width: 250, height: 50, alignment: .center)","}"]},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set the minimum scale factor to any value greater than "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less than or equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":". The default value is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenSwiftUI uses this value to shrink text that doesn’t fit in a view when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it’s okay to shrink the text. For example, a label with a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"minimumScaleFactor"},{"type":"text","text":" of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.5"},{"type":"text","text":" draws its text in a font size as small as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"half the actual font if needed."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui","type":"topic","title":"OpenSwiftUI","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Declare the user interface and behavior for your app on every platform."}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/EnvironmentValues/minimumScaleFactor":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"minimumScaleFactor","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"minimumScaleFactor","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/environmentvalues\/minimumscalefactor","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EnvironmentValues\/minimumScaleFactor","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The minimum permissible proportion to shrink the font size to fit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the text into the available space."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/EnvironmentValues":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"EnvironmentValues"}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/environmentvalues","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection of environment values propagated through a view hierarchy."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EnvironmentValues","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"EnvironmentValues"}],"type":"topic","title":"EnvironmentValues"}}}